headline: Unlocking Q4 Potential of Darden Restaurants (DRI): Exploring Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top -and-bottom-line estimates for Darden Restaurants (DRI), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended May 2025.

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock to Target This Week and 2 to Think Twice About
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
